works.description: Much of the content on this page was scraped from our article, identified below.  Specifically, everything from "How and Where to Fish Crankbaits For Bass" and below was copied from our site.

Everything on this page is pieced-together content stolen from other sites.  For example, everything from the line "In the summer, when bass are hitting crankbaits in the morning and then stop, switch to a grub." on down is stolen from BassResource.com.  

Search for snippets of copy above that to find the other original sites and content.
